title: FIGHT FOR ZELDA - Hyrule Total War Mod Gameplay
description:
Hyrule Total War Mod Gameplay - This is my first look at Hyrule Total War.  In the beginning of the video I talk about what I think about the mod, and show off some custom settlements.  Then we take on the Stalfos as the Kingdom of Hyrule.  Enjoy the Video :D

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
